# Bootload Modifier тАФ Full Change Log

> Complete record of everything built, fixed, and changed across all development sessions.

---

## Project Overview

Bootload Modifier (BLM) is a cross-platform boot entry manager.
It lets advanced users and IT professionals safely view, rename, delete, reorder,
and change the default boot entry across GRUB2, systemd-boot, Windows BCD, and macOS
тАФ without touching config files manually.

**Total codebase: ~5,000 lines** (excluding `third_party/`)

---

