## Session 27 тАФ Buttons Greyed Out + Settings Tab Incomplete

### Bug 65 тАФ Up/Down/Rename buttons greyed out due to writable race condition

`doRefresh()` fires `listEntries` and `backendInfo` simultaneously. `listEntries`
responds first тАФ the user sees entries and immediately tries to click a button
тАФ but `backendInfo` has not yet fired, so `app.writable` is still `false`.
All buttons requiring `canWrite` are greyed.

**Fix:** When `listEntries` succeeds and entries are non-empty, immediately set
`app.writable = true`. The `backendInfo` callback confirms or corrects the value
when it arrives.

Settings tab expanded to four sections matching the Python version:
Behaviour, Mode, File paths, Backend.

---

## Session 28 тАФ Unicode Rendering Fix, Detail Panel Polish

### Bug 66 тАФ Unicode symbols render as `?` on Windows

Nuklear's built-in bitmap font covers ASCII 32тАУ127 only.

**Fix:** Replaced all Unicode symbols with ASCII equivalents:

| Was | Now |
|---|---|
| `тШЕ` (default marker) | `[default]` |
| `тЪа` (read-only label) | `[read-only]` |

Detail panel: horizontal rule between name and fields, label column widened to 100px,
status badges in their own section, field row height increased to 20px.

